150 - #TGIF folks! Here’s a good deal to share with you guys - Fancy some really delectable Asian OG wok-fried cuisines and handmade rolls that are pretty popular all around these days? You can expect bold and cheeky flavours in the name of Asian cuisine delivered to your doorstep from @woknrollsg! ✨ // I’ll personally recommend the WOK Chilli Crab Noodles and the WOK Black Pepper Angus Beef. Superb flavor and beef tenderness on point. 💯.
.
